{"content": "I need to multiply 380\u2089 \u00d7 311\u2089.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n380\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 8\u00d79\u00b9 + 0\u00d79\u2070 = 3\u00d781 + 8\u00d79 + 0\u00d71 = 243 + 72 + 0 = 315\u2081\u2080\n\n311\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 1\u00d79\u00b9 + 1\u00d79\u2070 = 3\u00d781 + 1\u00d79 + 1\u00d71 = 243 + 9 + 1 = 253\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n315 \u00d7 253 = 79,695\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n79695 \u00f7 9 = 8855 r 0\n8855 \u00f7 9 = 983 r 8\n983 \u00f7 9 = 109 r 2\n109 \u00f7 9 = 12 r 1\n12 \u00f7 9 = 1 r 3\n1 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 1\n\nReading from bottom to top: 131280\u2089\n\n**131280**", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1150, "completion_tokens": 324}